{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839119071,"sessionID":"ses_287bf31a7ffefWSUdz2WISoq65","part":{"id":"prt_d78428682001ZYzL4P6Y7EF5gf","messageID":"msg_d78415cb1001mOgVmJ5vv1bfwM","sessionID":"ses_287bf31a7ffefWSUdz2WISoq65","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-b4955aed5ac540ab8d666a8bce715da6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-001 Task Checklist: CRD AgentRuntime ń▒╗Õ×ŗÕ«Üõ╣ē\n\n## Status\nStage: ST-3 (Design) - Completed  \nPhase: ST-4 (Implementation) - In Progress\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Type Definition\n### [ ] TASK-001: Create package directory structure\n**Description**: Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` directory structure for CRD type definitions.\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ntest -d pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 && echo \"Directory exists\" || echo \"Directory missing\"\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- Directory `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` exists\n- Directory is writable and follows Go package conventions\n\n---\n\n### [ ] TASK-002: Define TargetPort helper type\n**Description**: Create `TargetPort` struct with port, protocol, name, and pathPrefix fields.\n\n**Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n\n**Requirements**:\n- `Port int32` - required field with validation markers for 1-65535 range\n- `Protocol string` - required enum validation for \"HTTP\"|\"HTTPS\"\n- `Name string` - optional field\n- `PathPrefix string` - optional field\n- JSON tags use camelCase\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestTargetPort\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- `TargetPort` struct compiles without errors\n- `Port` field has `+kubebuilder:validation:Minimum=1` and `+kubebuilder:validation:Maximum=65535` markers\n- `Protocol` field has `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS` marker\n- JSON tags are correctly formatted\n\n---\n\n### [ ] TASK-003: Define PodTemplateSpec helper type\n**Description**: Create `PodTemplateSpec` struct with metadata and spec fields.\n\n**Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n\n**Requirements**:\n- `Metadata metav1.ObjectMeta` - optional field\n- `Spec PodSpec` - optional field\n- Reuses Kubernetes core v1 types\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestPodTemplateSpec\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- `PodTemplateSpec` struct compiles without errors\n- Fields reference Kubernetes core v1 types correctly\n- JSON tags use camelCase\n\n---\n\n### [ ] TASK-004: Define AgentRuntimeSpec\n**Description**: Create `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct with all required fields and default values.\n\n**Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n\n**Requirements**:\n- `MaxSessionDuration string` - default \"8h\"\n- `SessionTimeout string` - default \"15m\"\n- `TargetPort []TargetPort` - minimum 1 item required\n- `PodTemplate PodTemplateSpec` - required field\n- Default value markers: `+kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"` and `+kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"`\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestAgentRuntimeSpec\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct compiles without errors\n- Default value markers are correctly applied\n- Required fields are properly tagged\n- `TargetPort` has `+kubebuilder:validation:MinItems=1` marker\n\n---\n\n### [ ] TASK-005: Define AgentRuntimeStatus\n**Description**: Create `AgentRuntimeStatus` struct with conditions and observed generation.\n\n**Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n\n**Requirements**:\n- `Conditions []metav1.Condition` - optional field\n- `ObservedGeneration int64` - optional field\n- Follows Kubernetes status conventions\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestAgentRuntimeStatus\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- `AgentRuntimeStatus` struct compiles without errors\n- `Conditions` field uses standard Kubernetes `metav1.Condition` type\n- JSON tags use camelCase with `omitempty` for optional fields\n\n---\n\n### [ ] TASK-006: Define AgentRuntime main type\n**Description**: Create `AgentRuntime` struct with TypeMeta, ObjectMeta, Spec, and Status.\n\n**Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n\n**Requirements**:\n- Embeds `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta`\n- Contains `Spec AgentRuntimeSpec` and `Status AgentRuntimeStatus`\n- Kubebuilder markers:\n  - `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`\n  - `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`\n  - `+kubebuilder:resource:shortName=art`\n  - `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"`\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestAgentRuntime\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- `AgentRuntime` struct compiles without errors\n- All kubebuilder markers are present and correct\n- ShortName \"art\" is configured\n- Print column for Age is configured\n\n---\n\n### [ ] TASK-007: Define AgentRuntimeList type\n**Description**: Create `AgentRuntimeList` struct for collection operations.\n\n**Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n\n**Requirements**:\n- Embeds `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ListMeta`\n- Contains `Items []AgentRuntime`\n- Has `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` marker\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestAgentRuntimeList\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- `AgentRuntimeList` struct compiles without errors\n- `Items` field is properly typed as `[]AgentRuntime`\n- Kubebuilder root object marker is present\n\n---\n\n### [ ] TASK-008: Create doc.go package documentation\n**Description**: Create `doc.go` with package-level markers for code generation.\n\n**Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go`\n\n**Requirements**:\n- Package comment describing the v1alpha1 runtime API\n- `+k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` marker\n- `+groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` marker\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ngrep -q \"k8s:deepcopy-gen=package\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go\ngrep -q \"groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- `doc.go` file exists\n- Contains required code generation markers\n- Package comment is present\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Scheme Registration\n### [ ] TASK-009: Create groupversion_info.go\n**Description**: Create `groupversion_info.go` with GroupVersion constants and SchemeBuilder.\n\n**Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go`\n\n**Requirements**:\n- Define `GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}`\n- Create `SchemeBuilder` using `scheme.Builder`\n- Export `AddToScheme` function\n- Export `Resource(resource string)` function\n- Has `+groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` marker\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestGroupVersionInfo\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- `GroupVersion` constant is correctly defined\n- `SchemeBuilder` and `AddToScheme` are exported\n- `Resource()` function returns correct `GroupResource`\n- Code compiles without errors\n\n---\n\n### [ ] TASK-010: Create register.go for scheme registration\n**Description**: Create `register.go` with kind/resource conversion functions and scheme setup.\n\n**Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`\n\n**Requirements**:\n- Define `SchemeGroupVersion` constant\n- Export `Kind(kind string)` function\n- Export `Resource(resource string)` function\n- Initialize `SchemeBuilder` and `localSchemeBuilder`\n- Export `AddToScheme` function\n- Register metav1 types in `init()` function\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestRegister\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- `SchemeGroupVersion` matches groupversion_info.go\n- `Kind()` and `Resource()` functions work correctly\n- `AddToScheme` function is exported and functional\n- metav1 types are registered in init()\n\n---\n\n### [ ] TASK-011: Register AgentRuntime types in scheme\n**Description**: Ensure `AgentRuntime` and `AgentRuntimeList` are registered in the scheme.\n\n**Implementation**: Modify `register.go` or create registration function\n\n**Requirements**:\n- Register `AgentRuntime` with correct `GroupVersionKind`\n- Register `AgentRuntimeList` with correct `GroupVersionKind`\n- Enable `DeepCopy` code generation\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestTypeRegistration\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- Types are registered in scheme\n- `runtime.Object` interface is implemented\n- `DeepCopy` methods will be generated\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: Code Generation\n### [ ] TASK-012: Generate DeepCopy methods\n**Description**: Run controller-gen to generate `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`.\n\n**Command**:\n```bash\ncontroller-gen object paths=\"./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...\"\n```\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ntest -f pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go && echo \"DeepCopy methods generated\" || echo \"Generation failed\"\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` file exists\n- Contains `DeepCopy()` methods for all types\n- Contains `DeepCopyInto()` methods for all types\n- Contains `DeepCopyObject()` methods implementing `runtime.Object`\n- No compilation errors in generated code\n\n---\n\n### [ ] TASK-013: Test DeepCopy methods\n**Description**: Write and run tests to verify DeepCopy methods work correctly.\n\n**Test File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types_test.go`\n\n**Test Cases**:\n- Test `DeepCopy()` creates independent copies\n- Test modifications to copy don't affect original\n- Test nested structs are deep copied\n- Test slice fields are deep copied\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestDeepCopy -v\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- All DeepCopy tests pass\n- Copies are independent from originals\n- No shared references between